  "text": "Furthermore, SimaticScan goes beyond simply identifying \"potential\" vulnerabilities to verifying the existence of these vulnerabilities in the PLC under consideration. Through experimentation in a comprehensive water treatment testbed [CITATION_1] , we demonstrate SimaticScan's effectiveness in determining a range of vulnerabilities across three distinct PLCs, including a previously unknown vulnerability in one of the PLCs 1 . Our experiments also show that SimaticScan outperforms the widely used Nessus vulnerability scanner (with relevant ICS-specific plugins deployed).",
